dc_title_s: Land Use Monroe County, WI YE2016
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Monroe County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Monroe_LandUse_YE2016.gdb'.[Prepared in 2010 from aerial imagery and other available data for the Monroe County Comprehensive Plan document. The Monroe County Comprehensive Plan was prepared by Crispell-Snyder, Inc. under the direction of the Monroe County Zoning Committee.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
